HEADWORD: Tetramera
<hw>Te*tram"e*ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Tetramerous</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A division of
